This is a nodejs app with the name todo app;

In order to run it in your computer,
you shold:
1 install nodejs and npm on your omputer;
2 install mongoDB and run it;
3 go to the project folder which this README file resides
and run npm init [npm will install the dependencies automatically for you according to the package.json];
4 open your browser and type http://127.0.0.1:3000 in your address bar;
5 enjoy your journey!!
